- <i>Gracias</i>!

07:18.883 --> 07:22.733
Meant to say, I think there's something
over there for ya. Just arrived.

07:31.333 --> 07:32.525
Just a bit of fun.

07:32.725 --> 07:35.243
Yeah, yeah, it's...

07:35.343 --> 07:37.309
You had me fooled there for a second.

07:52.192 --> 07:53.368
So?

07:53.468 --> 07:55.536
I go for dinner with this guy
the other night.

07:55.937 --> 07:57.753
- The pharmacy guy?
- Oh, please!

07:57.853 --> 08:01.262
