- You always said Ireland was small.

09:31.637 --> 09:33.395
Yeah, I did warn ya.

09:34.895 --> 09:39.150
- We should probably hug or something.
- Yeah, don't mind.

09:39.250 --> 09:41.141
Okay.

09:41.595 --> 09:44.538
- Are we hugging?
- Sorry. I thought you didn't want to.

09:44.638 --> 09:48.637
- Definitely. Or whatever.
- Okay.

09:58.195 --> 10:02.045
