tourist office, I'll give you that.

10:02.145 --> 10:05.435
I've just got to run down
to the bank before lunch.

10:05.535 --> 10:07.881
There was a message for ya.

10:08.562 --> 10:10.034
Thanks.

10:12.028 --> 10:15.303
