- Cool.

10:17.912 --> 10:19.753
If I get it.

10:19.853 --> 10:22.237
And you work here?

10:22.337 --> 10:26.163
- Yeah, it's grand, you know.
- Where's the toilets?

10:27.637 --> 10:30.796
They're right over there.
Just down there.

10:34.028 --> 10:36.740
That's great. You're doing well.

10:37.228 --> 10:38.753
What are you doing here?

10:38.853 --> 10:43.828
We had an electrical problem en route.
So the plane had to land here.

10:43.928 --> 10:47.695
I'm on standby for a flight tonight
or tomorrow, but I need a room.

10:47.795 --> 10:51.162
- Do you guys do that here?
- Just say the word.

10:54.062 --> 10:56.514
Christ! Sorry!

10:59.188 --> 11:02.953
Flynn's Hotel. They have a room.

11:08.228 --> 11:10.545
