11:38.037 --> 11:41.433
- Happy Valentine's Day.
- You too.

11:48.620 --> 11:50.553
So you do what to this girl?

11:50.653 --> 11:55.007
We worked together about eight years ago.
I was on a student visa in the States.

11:55.107 --> 11:56.703
You love her?

11:57.403 --> 12:01.873
There was talk of me staying,
maybe getting hitched.

12:03.887 --> 12:04.862
Married.

12:04.962 --> 12:07.078
